com.snapbundle.model.base

Interface IReferentialObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAccountContext
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IFile, IMetadata, INotificationEndpoint, IObjectInteraction, IRelationship, ITagAssignment, ITimelineEntry
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    File, Metadata, NotificationEndpoint, ObjectInteraction, ReferentialObject, Relationship, TagAssignment, TimelineEntry, TypeSafeMetadata

    public interface IReferentialObject
extends IAccountContext
    Defines an explicit relationship between two otherwise disparate domain resources within the same account context. The pairing is always based on the combination of the EntityReferenceType and the system-assigned URN, the "reference urn."
